<script type="e714ff8a52e381521d174786-text/javascript">
window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || []

var shopNameElement = document.querySelector('[data-seller-selected]')
var shopName = shopNameElement && shopNameElement.textContent

function addToCartDataLayer () {
  const integers = '3.949'.replace('.', '')
  const price = integers + '.90'

  window.dataLayer.push({
    'event': 'addToCart',
    'ecommerce': {
      'currencyCode': 'BRL',
      'add': {
        'products': [{
          'name': 'Ar condicionado Split 24000 BTUs Quente e Frio 220V Series A1 TCL',
          'id': '91697550',
          'price': price,
          'brand': 'TCL',
          'category': 'climatizacao-e-ventilacao/ar-condicionado',
          'quantity': 1,
          'dimension8': 'delivery',
          'dimension15': shopName
        }]
      }
    }
  })
}

</script>
